00:43:56.159 --> 00:44:02.560
Traditionally, the system admin has control of your system library, and then your users have

00:44:02.560 --> 00:44:10.320
control of your user libraries, and that tends to be what we recommend today.

00:44:10.320 --> 00:44:15.679
That's kind of the de facto standard. I think in the future, we'll have better organization

00:44:15.679 --> 00:44:21.679
around libraries and how they interact with projects so that things become more reproducible.

00:44:26.159 --> 00:44:26.800
Thank you.

